// SPEC-CBTC-ZK-FUNGIBILITY-AMENDMENT §5.25 — T_SLOT_MERGE decoder.
// Inverse of SPLIT: consumes N (2..16) old slots and produces one new slot
// at K_btc_new = new_recipient_commit − denom_new·H, with denom_new ≤ Σ
